Acknowledgments
----------------

This project is a pure Rust port of the Haskell cardano-base library
maintained by Intersect MBO. We are grateful to the original authors
and maintainers for their work on the cryptographic foundations of
the Cardano blockchain.

Original Haskell repository:
<https://github.com/IntersectMBO/cardano-base>

This Rust implementation maintains binary compatibility with the
Haskell version while providing the safety and performance benefits
of the Rust programming language.
